  "Invoke 'macroexpand-1' on the expression at point.
If invoked with a PREFIX argument, use 'macroexpand' instead of
'macroexpand-1'."
  (interactive "P")
  (let ((expander (if prefix 'macroexpand 'macroexpand-1)))
